metadata.name: Birb Mass
metadata.description:
People like a mass of birbs because they are incredibly adorable and fun to look at. Birbs are small, colorful birds that often have vibrant feathers and unique patterns. They come in a variety of shapes and sizes, and they often have silly expressions and poses that make them even cuter. 

Watching a flock of birbs interacting with each other is also quite entertaining, as they often perform whimsical stunts together. Birbs are also symbols of freedom and joy, which is why many people find them so appealing.

Made with Disco Diffusion, description by GPT-3.
